#: ../../activity.rst:5
msgid "Using the Activity app"
msgstr "Ag baint úsáide as an aip Gníomhaíochta"

#: ../../activity.rst:7
msgid ""
"The Activity app keeps track of everything happening in your Nextcloud. It "
"records events such as file changes, shares, calendar updates, and more, "
"giving you a chronological overview of what happened and when."
msgstr ""
"Coinníonn an aip Gníomhaíochta súil ar gach rud a tharlaíonn i do Nextcloud."
" Taifeadann sé imeachtaí ar nós athruithe comhad, comhroinnt, nuashonruithe "
"féilire, agus tuilleadh, ag tabhairt forbhreathnú croineolaíoch duit ar a "
"tharla agus cathain."

#: ../../activity.rst:11
msgid "The Activity app is enabled by default."
msgstr "Tá an aip Gníomhaíochta cumasaithe de réir réamhshocraithe."

#: ../../activity.rst:15
msgid "*The Activity stream showing all recent activities.*"
msgstr ""
"*An sruth Gníomhaíochta a thaispeánann na gníomhaíochtaí le déanaí go léir.*"

#: ../../activity.rst:19
msgid "Viewing your activity stream"
msgstr "Ag féachaint ar do shruth gníomhaíochta"

#: ../../activity.rst:21
msgid ""
"To view your activity stream, click on the **Activity** icon in the top "
"navigation bar or navigate to ``/apps/activity`` in your browser."
msgstr ""
"Chun do shruth gníomhaíochta a fheiceáil, cliceáil ar an deilbhín "
"**Gníomhaíocht** sa bharra nascleanúna uachtarach nó téigh chuig "
"``/apps/activity`` i do bhrabhsálaí."

#: ../../activity.rst:24
msgid ""
"The stream shows all events grouped by day. Each entry shows what happened, "
"which file or object was affected, and how long ago the event occurred. "
"Entries from other apps such as Calendar, Contacts, or Talk also appear in "
"the stream if those apps are installed."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann an sruth na himeachtaí go léir grúpáilte de réir lae. "
"Taispeánann gach iontráil cad a tharla, cén comhad nó réad a raibh tionchar "
"air, agus cé chomh fada ó shin a tharla an teagmhas. Feictear iontrálacha ó "
"aipeanna eile ar nós Féilire, Teagmhálaithe, nó Talk sa sruth freisin má tá "
"na haipeanna sin suiteáilte."

#: ../../activity.rst:31
msgid "Filtering activities"
msgstr "Gníomhaíochtaí scagtha"

#: ../../activity.rst:33
msgid "The left sidebar provides filters to narrow down the activity stream:"
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an taobhbharra clé scagairí ar fáil chun an sruth gníomhaíochta a "
"chúngú:"

#: ../../activity.rst:35
msgid "**All activities** shows everything."
msgstr "Taispeánann **Gach gníomhaíocht** gach rud."

#: ../../activity.rst:36
msgid "**By you** shows only activities that you triggered yourself."
msgstr "Ní thaispeánann **Tusa** ach gníomhaíochtaí a spreag tú féin."

#: ../../activity.rst:37
msgid "**By others** shows only activities triggered by other users."
msgstr ""
"Ní thaispeánann **Ó dhaoine eile** ach gníomhaíochtaí arna spreagadh ag "
"úsáideoirí eile."

#: ../../activity.rst:38
msgid ""
"**File changes** shows only file and folder events (create, modify, delete, "
"rename, move)."
msgstr ""
"Ní thaispeánann **Athruithe comhaid** ach imeachtaí comhad agus fillteán "
"(cruthú, modhnú, scriosadh, athainmniú, bogadh)."

#: ../../activity.rst:41
msgid ""
"Additional filters may appear depending on which apps are installed on your "
"Nextcloud instance (e.g. **Favorites**, **Calendar**, **Contacts**)."
msgstr ""
"D’fhéadfadh scagairí breise teacht chun cinn ag brath ar na haipeanna atá "
"suiteáilte ar d’eispéireas Nextcloud (m.sh. **Is Fearr Liom**, **Féilire**, "
"**Teagmhálaithe**)."

#: ../../activity.rst:47
msgid "*The activity stream filtered to show only your own activities.*"
msgstr ""
"*Scagadh an sruth gníomhaíochta chun do ghníomhaíochtaí féin amháin a "
"thaispeáint.*"

#: ../../activity.rst:51
msgid "*The activity stream filtered to file changes only.*"
msgstr ""
"*Sruth na gníomhaíochta scagtha chun athruithe comhaid amháin a fheiceáil.*"

#: ../../activity.rst:55
msgid "Activity in the Files sidebar"
msgstr "Gníomhaíocht sa bharra taoibh Comhad"

#: ../../activity.rst:57
msgid ""
"You can also view activities for a specific file or folder directly from the"
" Files app. Select a file, open the sidebar and click on the **Activity** "
"tab. This shows only the events related to that particular file, such as "
"when it was created, modified, shared, or tagged."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat féachaint ar ghníomhaíochtaí le haghaidh comhaid nó fillteáin"
" ar leith go díreach ón aip Comhad freisin. Roghnaigh comhad, oscail an "
"barra taoibh agus cliceáil ar an táb **Gníomhaíocht**. Ní thaispeánann sé "
"seo ach na himeachtaí a bhaineann leis an gcomhad sin, amhail cathain a "
"cruthaíodh, a modhnaíodh, a roinneadh nó a clibeáladh é."

#: ../../activity.rst:65
msgid "*The Activity tab in the Files sidebar showing per-file events.*"
msgstr ""
"*An cluaisín Gníomhaíochta sa bharra taoibh Comhad a thaispeánann imeachtaí "
"in aghaidh an chomhaid.*"

#: ../../activity.rst:69
msgid "RSS feed"
msgstr "Fotha RSS"

#: ../../activity.rst:71
msgid ""
"The Activity app can provide your activity stream as an RSS feed, allowing "
"you to follow your Nextcloud activity from any feed reader."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leis an aip Gníomhaíochta do shruth gníomhaíochta a sholáthar mar "
"bheatha RSS, rud a ligeann duit do ghníomhaíocht Nextcloud a leanúint ó aon "
"léitheoir beatha."

#: ../../activity.rst:74
msgid "To enable the RSS feed:"
msgstr "Chun an fotha RSS a chumasú:"

#: ../../activity.rst:76
msgid "Open the Activity app."
msgstr "Oscail an aip Gníomhaíochta."

#: ../../activity.rst:77
msgid "Click **Activity settings** at the bottom of the left sidebar."
msgstr "Cliceáil **Socruithe gníomhaíochta** ag bun an bharra taoibh chlé."

#: ../../activity.rst:78
msgid "Enable the **Enable RSS feed** toggle."
msgstr "Cumasaigh an lascthach **Cumasaigh fotha RSS**."

#: ../../activity.rst:79
msgid "Copy the RSS feed link that appears."
msgstr "Cóipeáil an nasc chuig an bhfotha RSS a thaispeántar."

#: ../../activity.rst:81
msgid ""
"The RSS feed link contains a secret token. Do not share it with others, as "
"it provides unauthenticated access to your activity stream."
msgstr ""
"Tá comhartha rúnda sa nasc chuig an bhfotha RSS. Ná roinn le daoine eile é, "
"mar go dtugann sé rochtain neamhúdaraithe ar do shruth gníomhaíochta."

#: ../../activity.rst:87
msgid "Notification settings"
msgstr "Socruithe fógra"

#: ../../activity.rst:89
msgid ""
"You can choose how you want to be notified about different types of "
"activities. Go to **Settings** > **Personal** > **Notifications** to "
"configure your preferences."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat a roghnú conas is mian leat fógra a fháil faoi chineálacha "
"éagsúla gníomhaíochtaí. Téigh go **Socruithe** > **Pearsanta** > **Fógraí** "
"chun do chuid sainroghanna a chumrú."

#: ../../activity.rst:95
msgid "*Personal notification settings for the Activity app.*"
msgstr "*Socruithe fógra pearsanta don aip Gníomhaíochta.*"

#: ../../activity.rst:97
msgid ""
"The settings are organized by category (e.g. **Files**, **Sharing**, "
"**Calendar, contacts and tasks**). For each activity type you can choose to "
"receive:"
msgstr ""
"Tá na socruithe eagraithe de réir catagóire (m.sh. **Comhaid**, "
"**Comhroinnt**, **Féilire, teagmhálacha agus tascanna**). Maidir le gach "
"cineál gníomhaíochta is féidir leat a roghnú na nithe seo a leanas a fháil:"

#: ../../activity.rst:101
msgid "**Mail** notifications (email)"
msgstr "Fógraí **Post** (ríomhphost)"

#: ../../activity.rst:102
msgid "**Push** notifications (mobile and desktop)"
msgstr "Fógraí **Brú** (soghluaiste agus deisce)"

#: ../../activity.rst:104
msgid ""
"Check or uncheck the corresponding boxes to enable or disable notifications "
"for each activity type."
msgstr ""
"Seiceáil nó díthiceáil na boscaí comhfhreagracha chun fógraí a chumasú nó a "
"dhíchumasú do gach cineál gníomhaíochta."

#: ../../activity.rst:109
msgid "Email notification frequency"
msgstr "Minicíocht fógra ríomhphoist"

#: ../../activity.rst:111
msgid ""
"Below the notification matrix you can choose how often email notifications "
"are sent:"
msgstr ""
"Faoin maitrís fógraí is féidir leat a roghnú cé chomh minic a sheolfar "
"fógraí ríomhphoist:"

#: ../../activity.rst:114
msgid "**As soon as possible** sends an email shortly after each event."
msgstr ""
"**A luaithe is féidir** seolann siad ríomhphost go gairid i ndiaidh gach "
"imeachta."

#: ../../activity.rst:115
msgid "**Hourly** batches notifications and sends them once per hour."
msgstr ""
"Déanann **fógraí uair an chloig** a bhaisc agus a sheoladh uair san uair."

#: ../../activity.rst:116
msgid "**Daily** sends a single email per day."
msgstr "Seolann **gach lá** ríomhphost amháin in aghaidh an lae."

#: ../../activity.rst:117
msgid "**Weekly** sends a single email per week."
msgstr "Seolann **Seachtainiúil** ríomhphost amháin in aghaidh na seachtaine."

#: ../../activity.rst:121
msgid "Daily activity summary"
msgstr "Achoimre ar ghníomhaíocht laethúil"

#: ../../activity.rst:123
msgid ""
"You can enable a daily summary email that is sent every morning with an "
"overview of the previous day's activities. This option is available as a "
"separate toggle below the notification frequency setting:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat ríomhphost achoimre laethúil a chumasú a sheoltar gach maidin"
" ina bhfuil forbhreathnú ar ghníomhaíochtaí an lae roimhe sin. Tá an rogha "
"seo ar fáil mar lasc ar leithligh faoin socrú minicíochta fógraí:"

#: ../../activity.rst:127
msgid "Check **Send daily activity summary in the morning** to enable it."
msgstr ""
"Seiceáil **Seol achoimre ar ghníomhaíocht laethúil ar maidin** chun é a "
"chumasú."

#: ../../activity.rst:129
msgid ""
"The daily summary is independent of the per-event notifications above and "
"provides a convenient digest of all activity."
msgstr ""
"Tá an achoimre laethúil neamhspleách ar na fógraí in aghaidh an imeachta "
"thuas agus cuireann sé achoimre áisiúil ar fáil ar an ngníomhaíocht go léir."
